{"data":[{"date":"13:48 23/08","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain: T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng th\u00f4i L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 anh t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.</h2><h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018-372-195158.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018-372-195158.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Bahrain 19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8 (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Bahrain: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng U23 t\u1edbi ngh\u1ecbch c\u1ea3nh ASIAD</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Anh ra s\u00e2n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i U23 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c 7 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ASIAD 2018. Cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 g\u1ea7n 50 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p U23 Pakistan.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain Ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain Ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/photo1534837012119-153483701211986237603.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng 'm\u1ea5t t\u00edch' t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng thay cho ch\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL. Ngay c\u1ea3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 ph\u00fat, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Park Hang Seo ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, vi\u1ec7c thay Tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 v\u00ec l\u00fd do chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c, khi n\u00e0o c\u1ea7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00ec t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o s\u00e2n&quot; &ndash; nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo lu\u00f4n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra, d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n nghi ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf cho th\u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt t\u1ea1i HAGL. Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00edt h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o hay t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh ghi b\u00e0n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng &quot;h\u00edp&quot; so v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Tr\u01b0\u1eddng x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadm, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng th\u00f4i L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng th\u00f4i L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/3/Truoc-tran-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Bahrain-Toa-sang-thoi-Luong-Xuan-Truong!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1eefa m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Olympic Palestine \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu c\u00fap t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng Vinaphone v\u1eeba qua, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Tuy\u00ean Quang c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i. Anh thi\u1ebfu \u0111i nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng mang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn cao c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 do th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c anh b\u1ecb &lsquo;qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i&rsquo; t\u1ea1i CLB HAGL khi h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0o c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do th\u1ea7y Park kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i &lsquo;m\u00e0i s\u1ee9c&rsquo; \u1edf ASIAD, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 2, 3 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 xem th\u00eam k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea5t gi\u1eef Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park gi\u1ea5u b\u00e0i cho v\u00f2ng trong. Khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Quang H\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hay V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c m\u00e0 qu\u00ean m\u1ea5t Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3 khi anh v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u01a1n h\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m nh\u1ecbp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, chuy\u1ec1n xa ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 nguy hi\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp thu\u1ed9c d\u1ea1ng hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m &lsquo;c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh&rsquo; cho v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien ve Xuan Truong\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/doi-hinh-olympic-viet-nam-dau-bahrain-su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, &quot;c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh&quot; L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, khi m\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i&nbsp;ASIAD, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng nh\u1ecdc b\u1edfi anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec sau qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 v\u1eeba qua, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng &lsquo;h\u00edp&rsquo; ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ea1p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. H\u01a1n h\u1ebft hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i s\u1ebd nung n\u1ea5u th\u00eam quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong l\u00f2ng ch\u00e0ng trai x\u1ee9 Tuy\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 anh c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#xA;\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span><br>\r\n19h30 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-tu-tin-truoc-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-195110.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/hlv-bahrain-tu-tin-truoc-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-tu-tin-truoc-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-195110.html\">HLV Bahrain t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, HLV Samir Chammam tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-hinh-olympic-viet-nam-dau-bahrain-su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot-168-195087.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/doi-hinh-olympic-viet-nam-dau-bahrain-su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-hinh-olympic-viet-nam-dau-bahrain-su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot-168-195087.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u Bahrain: S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1edfi ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Park Hang...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5828","checkdouble":"195148"},{"date":"14:36 23/08","title":"Ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean t\u1ea7m Bahrain","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Santoso Estu \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb trang Bola Sport (Indonesia) nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd th\u1eafng Bahrain.</h2><h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018-372-195158.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018-372-195158.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Bahrain 19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8 (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Bahrain: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\nPh\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean t\u1ea7m Bahrain</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Bahrain ch\u1ec9 mang t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1 tr\u1ebb, v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 21 tu\u1ed5i, c\u00e1 bi\u1ec7t c\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ecd x\u00e1t cho nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn di\u1ec5n ra trong 2 n\u0103m n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean t\u1ea7m Bahrain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean t\u1ea7m Bahrain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Viettel_la_don_vi_dong_hanh_cung_VOV_mang_ASIAD_2018_ve_Viet_Nam_Anh_Nguyen_Khanh_Nguon_Viettel.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1eeda th\u1eafng \u0111ang m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u1eeb ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Santoso Estu \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb trang Bola Sport (Indonesia).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Bongdaplus, c\u00e2y vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD 2018 cho hay: &ldquo;Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. Sau VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc. Vi\u1ec7c Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Bahrain \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang n\u1eafm \u01b0u th\u1ebf h\u01a1n khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. T\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Bahrain, gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111i ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m h\u01a1n&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Santoso Estu c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Indonesia trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0 Th\u00e1i Lan, Myanmar \u0111ang c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Sau khi Malaysia th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf ASIAD 18, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Indonesia \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, trong khi Th\u00e1i Lan, Myanmar \u0111ang c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i th\u00ec m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Malaysia, Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Indonesia \u1edf ASIAD r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng kh\u00edch l\u1ec7&rdquo;, ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean n\u00e0y t\u00e2m s\u1ef1.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong-168-195148.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong-168-195148.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain: T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng th\u00f4i L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng!</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain-168-195141.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain-168-195141.html\">4 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5827","checkdouble":"195151"},{"date":"16:22 23/08","title":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/bong-da-viet-nam-dang-hon-thai-lan-o-diem-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo chuy\u00ean gia n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan sau nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ASIAD 2018, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, gi\u00e0nh 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n n\u00e0o. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng g\u00e2y ti\u1ebfng vang l\u1edbn khi ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, trong khi Th\u00e1i Lan m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Scott McIntyre cho r\u1eb1ng n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhan dinh Olympic Viet Nam vs Olympic Bahrain\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 e ng\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh. Nh\u01b0 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi. H\u1ecd g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, t\u1ea1o pressing t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;D\u00f9 sao, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi tr\u1ecdng \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ebb. Vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u00f4ng Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; tay vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a t\u1edd FOX Sports Asia cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qua nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01a1n Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay, trong gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u AFF Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong-168-195148.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong-168-195148.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain: T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng th\u00f4i L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng!</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/phong-vien-chu-nha-asiad-danh-gia-olympic-viet-nam-tren-tam-bahrain-168-195151.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/phong-vien-chu-nha-asiad-danh-gia-olympic-viet-nam-tren-tam-bahrain-168-195151.html\">Ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean t\u1ea7m Bahrain</span><br>\r\n\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean Santoso Estu \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb trang Bola Sport (Indonesia) nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain-168-195141.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain-168-195141.html\">4 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5826","checkdouble":"195152"},{"date":"15:11 23/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Bahrain 19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Bahrain: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD 2018 l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 23/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 VI\u1ec6T NAM VS U23 BAHRAIN C\u00d3 B\u1ea2N QUY\u1ec0N</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">LINK 1:&nbsp;<span href=\"https://fptplay.vn/livetv/vtc3-hd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://fptplay.vn/livetv/vtc3-hd</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\nLINK 2: <span href=\"https://vtc.gov.vn/kenh/vtc3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://vtc.gov.vn/kenh/vtc3</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\nLINK 3:&nbsp;<span href=\"https://vtc.gov.vn/kenh/vtc3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://vovtv.vov.vn</span></div>\r\n<br>\r\nLINK 4:&nbsp;<span href=\"https://vtv.vn/vtv6/truyen-hinh-truc-tuyen.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://vtv.vn/vtv6/truyen-hinh-truc-tuyen.htm</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng tin tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n- Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Bahrain t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 6 l\u1ea7n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn. Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng 5 v\u00e0 thua 1. <br>\r\n- \u1ede ASIAD, Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Bahrain 2 l\u1ea7n (th\u1eafng 1, thua 1). <br>\r\n- Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ghi 4 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Bahrain trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\n- N\u1ebfu ghi th\u00eam 1 b\u00e0n n\u1eefa, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ASIAD. <br>\r\n- 1/2 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Bahrain hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u1eebng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng U19 Bahrain thua U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/3-doi-hinh-co-the-duoc-thay-park-su-dung-o-dt-olympic-viet-nam-neu-thieu-dinh-trong-168-195162.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/dinhtrongngay238dl_jpau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/3-doi-hinh-co-the-duoc-thay-park-su-dung-o-dt-olympic-viet-nam-neu-thieu-dinh-trong-168-195162.html\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\n<span>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n sau khi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng chi\u1ec1u qua, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c HLV Park Hang Seo ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam....</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh vi\u1ebft n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch khi \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ASIAD 2018. N\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 8 \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n, tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch &lsquo;v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu&rsquo; trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u00eam Uzbekistan l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Bahrain b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Bahrain b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Viettel_la_don_vi_dong_hanh_cung_VOV_mang_ASIAD_2018_ve_Viet_Nam_Anh_Nguyen_Khanh_Nguon_Viettel.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1edf d\u0129 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u1eeda tr\u00ean t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 b\u1edfi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng l\u00e0m n\u00ean t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng 3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft. Ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng d\u00f9 trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nhau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Olympic Bahrain ch\u1ec9 mang \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U21 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang ta ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/3-doi-hinh-co-the-duoc-thay-park-su-dung-o-dt-olympic-viet-nam-neu-thieu-dinh-trong-168-195162.html\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/phong-vien-chu-nha-asiad-danh-gia-olympic-viet-nam-tren-tam-bahrain-168-195151.html\">Ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean t\u1ea7m Bahrain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong-168-195148.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain: T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng th\u00f4i L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain-168-195141.html\">4 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-khong-duoc-xem-nhe-bahrain-168-195112.html\">&ldquo;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u1eb9 Bahrain&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-tu-tin-truoc-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-195110.html\">HLV Bahrain t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-19h30-ngay-238-viet-tiep-ky-tich-168-195103.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain (19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8): Vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5825","checkdouble":"195158"},{"date":"15:44 23/08","title":"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/23/dinhtrongngay238dl_jpau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n sau khi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng chi\u1ec1u qua, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c HLV Park Hang Seo ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng?\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>1. Bi\u1ebfn V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0m trung v\u1ec7 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 nh\u1edd chi\u1ec1u cao l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1edfi \u00f4ng Park kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c V\u0103n H\u1eadu ph\u1ea3i \u2018\u1edf nh\u00e0\u2019\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hai \u0111\u00e0n anh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Bahrain c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1eefa c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i nh\u1eb1m ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c pha treo b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trong c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua, sau khi \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Park \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c\u00a0b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Khi \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Thanh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao l\u1ea1i cho Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u00f2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n sang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1m v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed V\u0103n H\u1eadu. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Bahrain ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/3-doi-hinh-co-the-duoc-thay-Park-su-dung-o-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi trung v\u1ec7 Th\u00e0nh Chung d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD, l\u00fac n\u00e0y trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho V\u0103n L\u1ee3i. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng khi anh \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 12 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017, L\u1ee3i \"Puyol\" \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang-seo ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 khi \u0111\u00f3, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1edd nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng t\u1ea1i V-League 2018, L\u1ee3i \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 l\u00f2ng tin c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u1ee3i l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd n\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 l\u00ec \u0111\u00f2n h\u01a1n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn V\u0103n L\u1ee3i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110TQG trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng xa.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/lineup-(1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<o:p></o:p></div>\r\n<h2>3. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 4-1-4-1. Khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 V\u0103n Thanh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Su\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao l\u1ea1i cho \u0110\u1ee9c Huy. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n t\u1eeb xa nh\u1eefng pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Bahrain.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i s\u1ee9c \u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Bahrain, v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e2ng l\u00ean qu\u00e1 cao, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00eanh m\u00f4ng hai bi\u00ean. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1edf s\u01b0\u1eddn, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng pha leo bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/lineup-(2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/link-sopcast/xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018-302-195163.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/link-sopcast/xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018-302-195163.html\">Link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Bahrain (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nLink xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Bahrain tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng link c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong-168-195148.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong-168-195148.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain: T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng th\u00f4i L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng!</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain-168-195141.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain-168-195141.html\">4 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5824","checkdouble":"195162"},{"date":"15:36 23/08","title":"Gia nh\u1eadp Bayern l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p Robben","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/23/arjen-robben-noi-ve-quyet-dinh-gia-nhap-bayern-munich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arjen Robben n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Bayern Munich. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Robben th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Bayern</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i Real Madrid, Arjen Robben gia nh\u1eadp Bayern Munich v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan h\u1ed3i sinh s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ngay m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Bayern gi\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG v\u00e0 c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, Robben c\u00f9ng Bayern li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng vinh quang. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 15 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 qua v\u1edbi 7 Bundesliga v\u00e0 1 Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arjen Robben n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arjen Robben n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/arjen-robben-noi-ve-quyet-dinh-gia-nhap-bayern-munich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Robben n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Bayern Munich</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00e3n nguy\u1ec7n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u0103m nay 34 tu\u1ed5i, Robben m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Bayern th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa. Anh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u00ean t\u00e2m c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. Arjen Robben n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Bayern Munich, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cBan \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d, Robben n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo ch\u1ee7 ngh\u0129a hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c v\u00e0 t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t nhanh. \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. Sau khi ra m\u1eaft Groningen v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i cho PSV \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 n\u0103m.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i: R\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 18. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i khi t\u00f4i 20 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi 3 n\u0103m \u1edf Chelsea, m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn. Sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 2 n\u0103m \u1edf Madrid tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Bayern ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cL\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ho\u00e0i nghi. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn hay kh\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/robert-lewandowski-phat-bieu-ve-bayern-munich-193-195085.html\">Lewandowski gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Bayern</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/bayern-munich-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-tu-tru-cot-193-194414.html\">Bayern Munich nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c vui t\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/thomas-muller-phat-bieu-ve-robert-lewandowski-193-194398.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Bayern kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real v\u00e0 M.U?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-frankfurt-05-bayern-munich-sieu-cup-duc-2018-330-194360.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Frankfurt 0-5 Bayern Munich (Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-jerome-boateng-khong-phai-lua-chon-hoan-hao-voi-mu-172-194042.html\">V\u00ec sao Jerome Boateng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi MU?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5823","checkdouble":"195157"},{"date":"15:05 23/08","title":"Barca l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n HLV Valverde","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/barca-len-ke-hoach-giu-chan-hlv-valverde.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV Ernesto Valverde, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Valverde ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Barca mang v\u1ec1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap danh hi\u1ec7u, g\u1ed3m ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga v\u00e0 c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 Vua T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u HLV Bilbao.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV Ernesto Valverde h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV Ernesto Valverde h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/barca-len-ke-hoach-giu-chan-hlv-valverde.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ernesto Valverde ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Valverde v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan, khi m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u HLV Bilbao.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mundo Deportivo, Barca mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV Ernesto Valverde, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00e1ng 10.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Eric Abidal l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1edfi Valverde mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Valverde \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n \u1edf Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Malcom, Arthur hay\u00a0Clement Lenglet. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Valverde \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Ousmane Dembele (21 tu\u1ed5i), Samuel Umtiti (24 tu\u1ed5i) hay Courtinho (26 tu\u1ed5i).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV valverde\" title=\"HLV valverde\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/hlv-valverde-khen-ngoi-malcom.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Valverde nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Bilbao \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n \u1edf Barca, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Camp Nou l\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. V\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga, BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n HLV Valverde mang v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan kh\u00f4ng \u0111i qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd b\u1ecb Roma lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5822","checkdouble":"195153"},{"date":"15:49 23/08","title":"Asensio \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/asensio-up-mo-kha-nang-chia-tay-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Marco Asensio kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Real nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Bernabeu trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><h2>Asensio \u00fap m\u1edf t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Asensio \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 8 danh hi\u1ec7u trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, bao g\u1ed3m 1 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga v\u00e0 2 danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAsensio \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi Real c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u. Nh\u01b0ng Asensio c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u00ean \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Asensio \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Asensio \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Asensio-up-mo-kha-nang-chia-tay-Real-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Marco Asensio \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cL\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Real Madrid. Sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cReal Madrid l\u00e0 CLB th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00e0 ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1eadp trung qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o t\u00f4i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd th\u00ec nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c d\u1ed3n l\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 th\u1ea5y b\u1edfi Real \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Asensio \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Lopetegui</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Lopetegui sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 \u00f4ng t\u1ea1o l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cLopetegui l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV c\u00f3 t\u01b0 duy b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp l\u00ean kh\u00e1 cao v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i d\u00ednh v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 do v\u00e0 di chuy\u1ec3n gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chi-36-trieu-bang-mua-iago-aspas-180-195164.html\">Real Madrid chi 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Iago Aspas</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-marcos-alonso-neu-180-195137.html\">Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Marcos Alonso n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5821","checkdouble":"195159"},{"date":"15:48 23/08","title":"PSG n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/22/psg-nang-gia-hoi-mua-rakitic-len-90-trieu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Rakitic c\u1ee7a Barca, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Rakitic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh PSG duy nh\u1ea5t Verratti l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, nh\u01b0ng Rabiot hay Thiago Motta kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa nh\u01b0 v\u1eady s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 90 tri\u1ec7u euro, PSG r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Rakitic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 90 tri\u1ec7u euro, PSG r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Rakitic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/22/Chi-90-trieu-euro,-PSG-rat-muon-mua-Ivan-Rakitic--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ivan Rakitic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Thomas Tuchel r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao. Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG quan t\u00e2m Ivan Rakitic c\u1ee7a Barca, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Barca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 Rakitic l\u00ean t\u1edbi 125 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 PSG kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Rakitic c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/ivan-rakitic-bat-ngo-ra-yeu-sach-voi-barca-180-195091.html\" target=\"_blank\">Rakitic \u0111ang \u0111\u00f2i t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi</span>, anh cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n kho\u1ea3n th\u00f9 lao 130.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Rakitic l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Rakitic c\u1ee7a Barca, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"PSG n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/4/6/PSG-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-Barca-len-90-trieu-euro-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Rakitic l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. 90 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 30 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Barca s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n kho\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady PSG mu\u1ed1n Barca nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, PSG s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00f2i 110 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Milinkovic-Savic, song PSG \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 80 ho\u1eb7c 90 tri\u1ec7u euro s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. PSG c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5820","checkdouble":"195161"},{"date":"16:12 23/08","title":"Real Madrid chi 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/23/real-madrid-chi-36-trieu-bang-mua-iago-aspas.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Iago Aspas c\u1ee7a Celta Vigo n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u0111i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Real Madrid \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chuan-bi-gui-loi-de-nghi-cuoi-cung-vu-eden-hazard-180-195067.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mu\u1ed1n mua Eden Hazard</span>, h\u1ecd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, song Chelsea v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Iago Aspas  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Iago Aspas  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Chi-36-trieu-bang,-Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Iago-Aspas--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Edinson Cavani (PSG), Radamel Falcao (Monaco), Robert Lewandowski (Bayern Munich), Rodrigo (Valencia)... l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, song kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, theo Don Balon, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Iago Aspas c\u1ee7a Celta Vigo n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIago Aspas t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Liverpool, song anh \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Celta Vigo. T\u1eeb n\u0103m 2015 \u0111\u1ebfn nay anh ra s\u00e2n 110 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi 55 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf La Liga, v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Iago Aspas</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Iago Aspas \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n, anh mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn thay v\u00ec ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ed9t CLB t\u1ea7m trung nh\u01b0 Celta Vigo.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid chi 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid chi 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/real-madrid-chi-36-trieu-bang-mua-iago-aspas.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid chi 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Iago Aspas</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Celta Vigo c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf La Liga c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb nay \u0111\u1ebfn khi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda, Real s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u01b0 Hazard hay Cavani kh\u00f4ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Iago Aspas ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5819","checkdouble":"195164"},{"date":"17:02 23/08","title":"M.U \u0111\u00f3n h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Spurs","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/mu-don-hang-loat-tru-cot-tro-lai-truoc-tran-gap-spurs.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Jose Mourinho c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng, khi M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau. Trong \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean tham gia chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1 tr\u1eadn. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Brighton b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Tottenham, 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh &ndash; Antonio Valencia v\u00e0 Nemanja Matic \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t. Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Mirror, c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed9p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y nu\u1ed1t tr\u1ecdng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng xung tr\u1eadn n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mourinho l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Matic v\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c\" title=\"M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Matic v\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/matic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Matic v\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, Valencia d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8. Matic, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i qua ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt, ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ngh\u1ec9 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Man United c\u0169ng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng t\u1eeb c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot. C\u1ea3 2 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V b\u1eb1ng d\u00f2ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1edbm t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Tottenham Hotspur, b\u1edfi v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fan-mu-thue-chuyen-co-giang-bieu-ngu-sa-thai-ed-woodward-172-195133.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/2/12/ceo-cua-mu-nhuc-dau-vi-thanh-tich-cua-leicester.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fan-mu-thue-chuyen-co-giang-bieu-ngu-sa-thai-ed-woodward-172-195133.html\">Fan M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 gi\u0103ng bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward</span><br>\r\nQu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward, v\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-mu-be-tac-y-tuong-tan-cong-o-mua-giai-thu-3-172-195132.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/vi-sao-mu-be-tac-y-tuong-tan-cong-o-mua-giai-thu-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-mu-be-tac-y-tuong-tan-cong-o-mua-giai-thu-3-172-195132.html\">V\u00ec sao M.U b\u1ebf t\u1eafc \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3?</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho t\u1eeb ph\u00eda M.U gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e9m, sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5818","checkdouble":"195168"},{"date":"17:24 23/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00ea Wenger kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Emery","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/them-mot-cau-thu-che-wenger-khong-bang-emery.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 tr\u1ea3i qua 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, nh\u01b0ng sao tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 HLV Emery b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nIwobi b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c Emery<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, &ldquo;Gi\u00e1o s\u01b0&rdquo; Wenger \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia Unai Emery \u0111\u1ebfn thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u kh\u1ea3 quan. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Premier League khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u1ea1i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, sao tr\u1ebb Iwobi cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111em l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho t\u00f4i (so v\u1edbi th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Wenger). \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y s\u1eafc b\u00e9n h\u01a1n, gi\u1eef phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111ang th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 HLV Emery sau 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp\" title=\"Iwobi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/them-mot-cau-thu-che-wenger-khong-bang-emery.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sao tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 HLV Emery sau 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y (Emery), t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u00fa v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Emery, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u00f3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho Arsenal, b\u1edfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i di\u1ec5n ra, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, d\u00f9 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1eed th\u00e1ch v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i&rdquo; &ndash; Alex Iwobi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 HLV Emery.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-arsenal-khich-le-leno-khi-mat-vi-tri-ve-tay-cech-172-195125.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/sao-arsenal-khich-le-leno-khi-mat-vi-tri-ve-tay-cech.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-arsenal-khich-le-leno-khi-mat-vi-tri-ve-tay-cech-172-195125.html\">Sao Arsenal kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 Leno khi m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1ec1 tay Cech</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Shkodran Mustafi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khi t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Unai Emery tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Emirates.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ashley-cole-danh-gia-trai-nguoc-arsenal-va-chelsea-nam-nay-172-195111.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/ashley-cole-danh-gia-trai-nguoc-arsenal-va-chelsea-nam-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ashley-cole-danh-gia-trai-nguoc-arsenal-va-chelsea-nam-nay-172-195111.html\">Ashley Cole \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u0103m nay</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5817","checkdouble":"195169"},{"date":"17:30 23/08","title":"G\u00f3c Liverpool: Th\u00e1i t\u1eed so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 vua Man City?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/goc-liverpool-thai-tu-soan-ngoi-nha-vua-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu hy v\u1ecdng nh\u00e0 vua Manchester City b\u1ecb h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 kh\u1ecfi ngai v\u00e0ng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ni\u1ec1m tin ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o Liverpool s\u1eafm vai th\u00e1i t\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sau \u0111\u00e2y 9 th\u00e1ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u1eddi gian cho ph\u00e9p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mua b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tinh gi\u1ea3m \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Liverpool b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, tri\u1ec3n khai n\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh g\u1ecdn v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n trong khi s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u00f3a m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, theo \u0111u\u1ed5i duy nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup. H\u1ecd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n sau World Cup, \u00e2m th\u1ea7m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u1eb7ng nh\u00ecn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 mua s\u1eafm trong ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool \u1edf Premier League 201819 Th\u00e1i t\u1eed so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i vua ManCity h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool \u1edf Premier League 201819 Th\u00e1i t\u1eed so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i vua ManCity h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Liverpool-o-Premier-League-201819-Thai-tu-soan-ngoi-vua-ManCity-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u1edf Premier League 2018/19 \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Crystal Palace ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu trong t\u00e2m tr\u00ed m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau The Kop, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t Selhurst Park ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t t\u1eebng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau ng\u00f3t ngh\u00e9t ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 h\u01a1n b\u1ed1n n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool, ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ec1 tay Man City m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t ra l\u00e0m sao. Burnley, Everton, Newcastle, Watford hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Swansea v\u00e0 West Brom \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u00f3 lu\u00f4n sa l\u1ea7y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-nghich-ly-cua-liverpool-logic-cua-chien-thang-172-195138.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/goc-nhin-nghich-ly-cua-liverpool-logic-cua-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-nghich-ly-cua-liverpool-logic-cua-chien-thang-172-195138.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nLiverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mang \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jurgen Klopp, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh n\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/alisson-becker-giai-ma-tan-binh-liverpool-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191660.html\" target=\"_blank\">Alisson Becker</span> ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, v\u1edbi phong th\u00e1i t\u1ef1 tin Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ed1ng v\u1eafng trong khung g\u1ed7 t\u1eeb bao l\u00e2u nay, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a b\u1eb1ng hai pha tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh t\u1eeb tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n. M\u1ea5t 8 tr\u1eadn n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 gi\u1edd, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t qu\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c b\u1eaft hay h\u01a1n v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d</em> \u2013 Gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac nh\u01b0 Jurgen Klopp c\u00f2n c\u1ee5t l\u1ee7n v\u00e0 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Loris Karius c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 \u00edt tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00f4ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn h\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c Liverpool Th\u00e1i t\u1eed so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 vua Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c Liverpool Th\u00e1i t\u1eed so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 vua Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Goc-Liverpool-Thai-tu-soan-ngoi-nha-vua-Man-City-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u1edf Premier League 2018/19 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh Naby Keita</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Naby Keita m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t s\u00e2u s\u1eafc h\u01a1n c\u1ea3. N\u1ed7i kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c v\u00e0 ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ng sinh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y \u1edf Anfield \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Guinea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n \u1edf ph\u00fat 22 khi Liverpool tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. Keita quay l\u01b0ng v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb Alisson, v\u1edbi c\u00fa gi\u1eadt g\u00f3t thi\u00ean t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Townsend lao l\u00ean t\u1eeb \u0111\u1eb1ng sau, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 v\u00e0 b\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebfn cho Salah \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hennessey.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00fat \u0111i m\u1ecdi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c pressing \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi g\u00e2y l\u00ean c\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, r\u00ea d\u1eaft v\u00e0i nh\u1ecbp v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i t\u1ef1 th\u00e2n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m cho Liverpool. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn trong v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 5 gi\u00e2y, c\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 ai \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi bi\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e3 h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh r\u01b0\u1ee3u vang v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-ve-naby-keita-phan-1-vua-cua-duong-pho-172-194447.html\">Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 Naby Keita (Ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u): Vua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-ve-naby-keita-phan-cuoi-giac-mo-cua-deco-de-nhi-172-194449.html\">Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 Naby Keita (Ph\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i): Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Deco \u0111\u1ec7 nh\u1ecb</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Keita kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o khi ch\u1ec9 \u00edt l\u00e2u sau, anh ch\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Townsend nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 an \u1ee7i b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp khi chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng sai \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 ngay ngo\u00e0i r\u00eca c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a x\u00e0 ngang khung th\u00e0nh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eb3ng quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u1eefng Kopites kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1ec1 h\u00e0 x\u00ed x\u00f3a cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1ed5n nh\u1ea5t hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, v\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1o ra cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, Keita mang \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, l\u00e0 c\u1ed9i ngu\u1ed3n \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi ng\u00f3c ng\u00e1ch tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch. B\u1ed7ng ch\u1ed1c, \u0111\u00f4i ba nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-duoc-khen-hay-hon-ca-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-172-194443.html\" target=\"_blank\">phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a N\u2019Golo Kante</span> d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 \u00edt n\u1ef1c c\u01b0\u1eddi h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool\" title=\"Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u1edf Premier League 2018/19: Th\u00e1i t\u1eed so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 vua Man City?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Liverpool v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh Selhurst Park c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t Crystal Palace v\u1ed1n ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n tay d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Roy Hodgson, m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Aaron Wan-Bissaka v\u00e0 Patrick Van Aanholt \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 hi\u1ec7u h\u00f3a h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Premier League, trong khi Mamadou Sakho v\u00e0 James Tomkins t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady \u00e1n ng\u1eef tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00eam h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp, b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0o qua 15 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t b\u00ean nhau, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu b\u00e0n thua m\u1ed7i 158 ph\u00fat. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn hai l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng trong 90 ph\u00fat.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Liverpool v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 Liverpool m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu hy v\u1ecdng nh\u00e0 vua Manchester City b\u1ecb h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 kh\u1ecfi ngai v\u00e0ng, ch\u1ec9 Liverpool m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eafm vai th\u00e1i t\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sau \u0111\u00e2y 9 th\u00e1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279653\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/8/21/liverpool-crystal-palace-100554359_1200_96.mp4&autoplay=false&urlParent=http://bongdanet.vn/video/crystal-palace-0-2-liverpool-premier-league-ngoai-hang-anh-vong-2-tbd71154\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h2><strong>Liverpool \u1edf Premier League 2018/19:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-liverpool-truoc-them-nha-201819-da-den-luc-nghi-ve-ngai-vang-172-193863.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-liverpool-truoc-them-nha-201819-da-den-luc-nghi-ve-ngai-vang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-liverpool-truoc-them-nha-201819-da-den-luc-nghi-ve-ngai-vang-172-193863.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Premier League 2018/19: \u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 ngai v\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\n28 n\u0103m, g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda \u0111\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00f4i qua, c\u00e1c C\u0110V trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1eabn m\u1ecfi m\u00f2n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5816","checkdouble":"195171"}]}